    "description": "<p>Total Manpower Pte. Ltd (UEN 202145012C) was incorporated&nbsp;in 2021.</p>\n<p>We provide both cleaning and manpower supply services. Our cleaning services include both part-time residential cleaning and commercial cleaning of F&amp;B outlets. The manpower services which we provide are stewards for events, public service attendants and hotel housekeeping staff.</p>\n<p>Total Manpower strives to provide effective&nbsp;communication to our clients, helping to ensure a professional and efficient relationship. Helping us to develop a continued relationship with which we can ensure optimum customer satisfaction with all services which we provide.</p>",
